author: adrianc
msg: Added a method to FindServices.java. The original code parses input parameters into a nested Map structure, then parses the nested Map structure into an EntityCondition. The new method takes a direct approach and parses input parameters directly into an EntityCondition. The method isn't used yet.

author: gstein
msg: Fix an erroneous use of svn_uri_is_child.
(report_revisions_and_depths): this is dealing with relpaths, so use the
right function. and since it is NOT a URI, then we don't need to decode.
